::Aerotaur::
    "Are you the cause of this?" he asks pointedly at Dinotron.  He alters 
his bow into a staff (as a bow without any arrows would be absurd) with two 
energon blades, one on each end.  This done he raises it and points it at 
Dinotron's head "And I suggest you answer me peacefully this time."
